c: 7
v: 165
t: "Tokkel meqe mari ken (Sabti Ayrót caddok tatre mara kinnuk) kassiiseh yanim cineeniih caben waqdi, umaanek waasak suge mara digaalak naggosneeh Sabti ayrót caddok tatraanamat sinni nafsi yudlume mara gibdi digaalay Qansarissah ken digaalele, Yallih amrik yewqe mara yekkeenimih sabbatah"